-H%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-RaTSZaUHzh49rWc6QXWeqw">Nhập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/T%C3%A2y-h%C3%A0-Kim-L%C4%83ng-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-Au8x0xwYW2LXafkG4bCq1w">Tây hà - Kim Lăng hoài cổ - 西河—金陵懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-aRbK_iKDMX5ibYXonb22rA">Chu Bang Ngạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C3%A1ng-du/poem-dLYEgwcQ7IbIIq24Mpcddw">Tráng du - 壯遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
